                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160529-81-off441 t18160529-81-cd442"></join>, and for stealing therein, four pieces of printed cotton containing ninety yards, value 12l. the goods of the said John Butterworth and 
                     
